## RADR program notice

This repository contains the **RADR (Recoilless Anti-Drone Rocket)** open
concept — documentation, structured data, and notional concept art for a
**Phase 0** mid-range counter-UAS engineering study.

- All specifications, performance figures, mass budgets, and mechanical
  descriptions are **notional** unless and until validated by test.
- Content is **not** authorization to procure, manufacture, export, field, or
  use any weapon system.
- Concept art and diagrams are **illustrative** design references, not build
  drawings or technical data packages.
- Third-party names (e.g. Evolution Space propellant reference) are cited for
  trade study context only; no endorsement is implied.

For prime teaming, development, or production licensing, use the partnership
guide and inquiry links above — not an informal email to the copyright holder
without a PCA.
